config MT_SND_SOC_6797
    bool "MT_SND_SOC_6797"
	default n
	help
		If you say Y, enable MT_SND_SOC_6797_driver.
		Must enable this to use medatek audio driver.
		The default value is y for MT6797.
		It's recommended no to change this.
